00:37:11,236 --> 00:37:12,404
Pak Kepala, di sini!

474
00:37:12,905 --> 00:37:14,656
Apa? Apa yang terjadi?

475
00:37:14,740 --> 00:37:15,782
Di sini!

476
00:37:17,034 --> 00:37:18,911
Dia masih bernapas?

477
00:37:19,453 --> 00:37:20,454
Dia sudah mati.

478
00:37:21,079 --> 00:37:24,291
Dia memasukkan halaman Alkitab
ke mulutnya hingga sesak napas.

479
00:37:29,504 --> 00:37:30,839
Bawa ke ruang perawatan.

480
00:38:13,841 --> 00:38:14,925
Lama tak bertemu.

481
00:38:15,759 --> 00:38:17,511
Kau menemukan bukti?

482
00:38:19,054 --> 00:38:20,305
Bagus sekali.

483
00:38:21,974 --> 00:38:23,308
Apa buktinya? Biar kulihat.

484
00:38:26,687 --> 00:38:27,729
Pak Park?

485
00:38:28,522 --> 00:38:29,940
Biar kulihat bukti itu.

486
00:38:32,943 --> 00:38:35,737
Salah satu tahanan bunuh diri.

487
00:38:37,698 --> 00:38:40,701
Pria yang sama yang kau coba bantu
beberapa saat lalu.

488
00:38:40,784 --> 00:38:41,785
Apa kau ingat?

489
00:38:44,246 --> 00:38:45,706
