547
00:42:06,323 --> 00:42:07,866
Dasar bajingan keparat.

548
00:42:09,701 --> 00:42:10,702
Di sini?

549
00:42:11,411 --> 00:42:12,829
Bagaimana caranya?

550
00:42:23,423 --> 00:42:25,092
Boleh kuberi saran?

551
00:42:26,385 --> 00:42:28,887
Tulislah surat wasiat
dan gantunglah dirimu.

552
00:42:29,471 --> 00:42:30,639
